Package: DSDprior
Title: Fitting latent Gaussian models with DSD priors for scales
Version: 0.0.1
Description: The package allows to fit latent Gaussian models with Gaussian and Bernoulli likelihoods using Design and Scale Depenend (DSD) priors for scale parameters. 
